OL,4,CExams remain 'best way' to guarantee
OL,5,Cstandards, experts say
OL,6, Anonymously-marked exam papers are
OL,7, still the best way of guaranteeing
OL,8, consistent standards in schools,
OL,9, according to a group of experts.
OL,11,FThe matter has been under close
OL,12,Fscrutiny since the last two exam diets
OL,13,Fwere scrapped because of the pandemic.
OL,15,FThe Scottish government is due to make
OL,16,Fa decision this month on whether next
OL,17,Fyear's exams will go ahead.
OL,19,FThe Commission on School Reform said
OL,20,Fcoursework was important but exams
OL,21,Favoided any unintentional bias.
